## 📄 Compliance Info
- **Spec**: OpenEnv v0.2.0+
- **Memory**: < 2GB (Judge-Ready for 8GB hardware)
- **Runtime**: FastAPI / Uvicorn
- **Evaluator Logs**: Strictly follows `[START]`, `[STEP]`, `[END]` format.

